{"tid":2279990,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"便衣警商場內圍捕毆打 男生：一開始以為係黑社會","createTime":"2020-11-10T07:24:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-11T17:56:16.000Z","uid":56115,"like":547,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":115,"replies":[{"pid":"86fc6cc25926fb9ad260169f42549d1ba1007f3e","tid":2279990,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-10T07:24:35.000Z","msg":"網民去年平安夜發起「和你Shop」活動，兩名男生當晚被指在尖沙嘴海港城內拒捕而被拘控，案件續審。其中一名被告男生自辯稱，當時遭警長從後用雙手大力箍頸，兩人雙雙倒地後，警長仍緊箍不放；而多名便衣警隨後走近他，不斷棍打他的頭部，他感呼吸困難，哀求「畀埋隻左手你鎖，你哋唔好再打」。惟有警員在上手銬後仍繼續毆打他。辯方問被告男生何時才知道他們是警員，男生直言：「直到上手銬嗰刻先估到，一開始以為係黑社會。」<br />\n<br />\n辯方呈堂的醫療報告顯示，被告頭部和前額均有血腫，右邊眼眉有1厘米長的裂傷，左臉有3厘米長的裂傷。另外呈堂照片顯示，事後被告頸部有瘀傷和擦傷。拘捕被告的便衣警10356曾耀華早前供稱，不能肯定被告傷勢從何而來。"},{"pid":"acc0d3181efe88d084cd66300597d91eccb1428d","tid":2279990,"uid":56115,"like":122,"dislike":18,"score":104,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-10T07:25:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201110/65K5JMWBDJAYPCF4BAIPNNPNRE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201110%2F65K5JMWBDJAYPCF4BAIPNNPNRE%2F&d=YlPq7SqekvAy96d0W8R9y9MQoCHxbgs64DeXVNsql00%3D&h=7f1bc660\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201110%2F65K5JMWBDJAYPCF4BAIPNNPNRE%2F&h=d95f02df\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201110/65K5JMWBDJAYPCF4BAIPNNPNRE/</a>"},{"pid":"b4ba554014a417337bdb7edbec9fc35a903f48c0","tid":2279990,"uid":376010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-10T07:25:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cfd6f4ad9f94bc67155917b64e0953b4c45bac73","tid":2279990,"uid":124983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-10T07:26:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb996c216d396b9b906dcf571e080db8f07d157d","tid":2279990,"uid":51820,"like":0,